[thinking] I'm thinking about how `build.gradle` has that `--initialize-at-run-time` setting. It seems that the class is initialized at runtime, not during the build phase. I wonder if the external workflow runs from a clean current commit should have covered this, but it didn’t. Maybe it’s because, after the second commit, `build.gradle` is still set for runtime initialization? It feels like I’m onto something here, but I need to double-check!
